ta and I=E2=80=99m going to be back in about 15 minutes,=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D =
Handler tells the Financial Times. =E2=80=9C=E2=80=98When I come back, just=
 give me one number and it=E2=80=99s the amount of money we lost. I want th=
e whole thing down by the time I come back.=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Jefferies escaped from Archegos=E2=80=99 collapse with=
 a modest $40mn loss while other banks were left on the hook for billions o=
f dollars.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CSometimes when you=E2=
=80=99re on vacation, there=E2=80=99s a clarity=E2=80=89.=E2=80=89.=E2=80=
=89.=E2=80=89because you=E2=80=99re not so close to the situation,=E2=80=9D=
 Handler says. =E2=80=9COur team did all the hard work by correctly identif=
ying the issue and quickly elevating it. You can just look at the big pictu=
re and make the decision.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px=
 0;">So probably not a swim-up bar, as I initially surmised? (Or a very lon=
g swim to the bar?) It is such a charming model of the chief executive offi=
cer=E2=80=99s role: You get talented empowered underlings, they do the work=
 and make the easy decisions, and they come to you for the hard calls, whic=
h you make while waiting for your drink. He should take more vacations.</p>=
